      <title>法国银行向农民提供优惠贷款利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/french-banks-to-offer-preferential-rates-on-loans-to-farmers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔表示，银行将向农民提供优惠贷款，作为政府努力化解农业危机的一部分，这场危机已引发数周的抗议活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/french-banks-to-offer-preferential-rates-on-loans-to-farmers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 13:01:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Orsted 首席执行官保持董事会执行扭亏为盈的信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/orsted-ceo-retains-confidence-of-board-to-execute-turnaround</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦能源巨头 Orsted A/S 完全相信，首席执行官 Mads Nipper 是带领公司在美国业务遭受重大损失并解雇两名高管后实现扭亏为盈的合适人选。]]></description>
